{"text_id":11404,"tokens":["##"," A"," Call"," for"," Direct"," Democracy",":"," Ab","ol","ishing"," the"," Electoral"," College","\n\n","The"," Electoral"," College"," system"," in"," the"," United"," States"," presidential"," elections"," has"," demonstra","bly"," failed"," to"," uphold"," democratic"," ideals","."," Its"," warped"," representation"," and"," vulnerability"," to"," manipulation"," compromise"," the"," integrity"," of"," elections"," and"," undermine"," the"," very"," essence"," of"," American"," democracy","."," It"," is"," imperative"," that"," the"," nation"," transition"," to"," a"," direct"," voting"," system",","," where"," the"," candidate"," who"," wins"," the"," popular"," vote"," becomes"," the"," president",".","\n\n","The"," Electoral"," College"," system"," perpetu","ates"," a"," power"," imbalance",","," where"," the"," electoral"," weight"," of"," certain"," states"," is"," unfairly"," inflated","."," This"," system"," unfairly"," biases"," the"," outcome"," in"," favor"," of"," larger"," states",","," regardless"," of"," their"," proportional"," population","."," This"," anachron","istic"," arrangement"," gives"," disproportion","ate"," influence"," to"," rural"," areas"," over"," urban"," centers",","," despite"," the"," reality"," that"," urban"," populations"," vastly"," out","number"," their"," rural"," counterparts",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," invites"," manipulation"," and"," potential"," tampering"," of"," results","."," By"," handing"," over"," the"," ultimate"," decision","-","making"," power"," to"," a"," select"," group"," of"," electors",","," the"," system"," becomes"," susceptible"," to"," coercion",","," bribery",","," or"," even"," fraud","."," This"," undermines"," the"," public","'","s"," faith"," in"," the"," fairness"," and"," transparency"," of"," elections",".","\n\n","A"," direct"," voting"," system"," would"," eliminate"," these"," flaws","."," By"," allowing"," citizens"," to"," cast"," their"," ballots"," directly"," for"," the"," president",","," the"," system"," ensures"," that"," the"," individual"," who"," garn","ers"," the"," most"," popular"," votes"," is"," elected","."," This"," system"," fosters"," transparency",","," accountability",","," and"," empowers"," ordinary"," citizens"," to"," have"," their"," voices"," heard",".","\n\n","The"," argument"," that"," a"," direct"," vote"," system"," would"," incentiv","ize"," \"","un","qualified"," candidates","\""," is"," unfounded","."," Qualified"," candidates"," still"," need"," to"," campaign",","," raise"," funds",","," and"," garner"," support"," from"," voters"," across"," the"," nation","."," A"," direct"," vote"," simply"," ensures"," that"," the"," candidate"," who"," resonates"," most"," with"," the"," people"," is"," elevated"," to"," office",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," is"," an"," outdated"," and"," und","em","ocratic"," relic","."," By"," transitioning"," to"," a"," direct"," voting"," system",","," the"," United"," States"," can"," strengthen"," its"," democracy",","," ensure"," fairness"," and"," transparency"," in"," elections",","," and"," empower"," the"," voices"," of"," the"," people","."," It"," is"," time"," to"," abandon"," the"," archaic"," practices"," of"," the"," past"," and"," embrace"," a"," system"," that"," truly"," reflects"," the"," will"," of"," the"," people","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}